        </p>
        <p>
            Please refer to the following guidelines when using the MonoGame logos:
            <ol>
                <li>The MonoGame logo can be used to link to the MonoGame project and credit MonoGame in your own works.</li>
                <li>
                    The MonoGame logo can be used only as a secondary brand in your own works, meaning the average viewer 
                    should know that this is not a MonoGame website, project, or publication. In short, don't use the 
                    MonoGame logo as your own logo.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The MonoGame logo can be printed on promotional products, such as t-shirts, as long as it's a 
                    secondary brand as described in point 2.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The MonoGame logo of your choice must be used <span class="fw-bold">unaltered and in original colors and typography.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    The MonoGame logo cannot be used on commercial products without explicit permission of the MonoGame team. 
                    Displaying the logo in your game credits is not considered commercial use.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </p>

